reviewText: Whether you're a 'US Navy Seal' fan, or if you're a Jeet Kune Do practitioner like myself. These kicking techniques and combos, will be very beneficial! Get this video ( hopefully, if there's anymore ), Drill Instructor Tucci, gives excellent tutelage and training!
